This is a fun puzzle elimination game!
You need to match three identical items on the same grill to complete the barbecue.
The difficulty increases level by level. Use your items wisely to clear stages more effectively!

Aim, throw, and survive! Be careful—avoid hitting other blades. The spinning wheel gets faster, the risks grow higher, and only your quick reflexes can keep you in the game. Can you beat the boss level and unlock epic knife skins? The challenge has begun!

Cute and vivid visuals make it more relaxing. 
Simple match-3 gameplay makes it quick to learn. 
Interesting power-ups and new characters provide a diverse and richer experience.

This is a brand new puzzle game, but with a twist on the original gameplay.
The goal is to clear all objects from the container to complete the current level.
The game grows increasingly challenging and requires strategic thinking to beat the clock.

The bus drives in the direction of the arrow.
If there is an obstacle, the bus cannot drive out.

Passengers in a certain color will only board the bus of that color.
The next passenger can only board after the first passenger gets on.

You win the game only when all passengers have boarded.
Let's take the challenge!

This is a casual puzzle game.
Find three identical fruits to make a glass of juice and turn all the fruits into juice.
The game is simple yet challenging, with gradually increasing difficulty!

Welcome to Cup Sorting Puzzle 3D!
A relaxing yet brain-teasing puzzle game!

Your mission: Sort the cups by color to make each stack perfectly uniform. Easy to learn but highly challenging – dive into multiple levels and unwind!

In this chill yet addictive 3D puzzle, organize cups by color. Exercise your brain and enjoy satisfying puzzle fun!
A relaxing but brain-teasing 2D logic game. Unscrew the bolts, sort the nuts, and assemble the wooden puzzle at your own pace—no time limits or pressure.

Unleash your shooting skills and break bricks in Shoot N Crush. This game is the best choice for your leisure time. Your goal is to shoot with precision and flexibility. Use the bouncing ball to smash a solid brick with precision. Each level has a different objective and difficulty, you need to break these bricks in the smartest way possible.

Play Sort Puzzle - Nuts and Bolts, a free and addictive sorting game! Train your brain by stacking nuts of the same color. Simple yet challenging, it's the perfect casual game to relax and sharpen your logic skills. Play now and start sorting!

Magci Flow are puzzle series solved by transferring liquids. Players must strategically use container capacities to sort liquids in the fewest moves. Tasks include merging same-colored liquids or precise sequencing, rigorously testing judgment skills.

Unlock 3D Cars: Traffic Puzzle is a traffic puzzle game featuring vibrant 3D graphics. Slide cars and buses within tight parking lots to free blocked vehicles. Each level simulates colorful traffic jams, testing your strategic planning. Complete levels to earn gold coins for unlocking car skins and power-ups. With simple controls and progressively challenging difficulty, the game also supports offline mode – perfect for commute breaks and leisure moments. Enjoy smooth animations and soothing background music designed to help you unwind while solving puzzles.
Sort colorful nuts onto matching bolts in this satisfying logic puzzle. Test your brain as you organize tools by color and complete each level with precision and strategy.

Combine at least 3 matching items to clear them from the board. The more items you combine at once, the better the rewards — including powerful boosters, special gifts, and handy extras! Work your way up the farm through increasingly challenging levels and see if you can complete the entire game. What are you waiting for? Jump in and enjoy the third sequel of the most beautiful Farm Match 3 game now!

Bubble it jam is a vibrant, fast-paced puzzle-shooter game where players aim and shoot colored balls to match and pop clusters of the same color.the goal is to collect color bubble, free the ropes, and complete each level. Every stage presents a new and exciting challenge, keeping gameplay fresh and engaging, combining strategy, quick reflexes, and a bit of luck for high scores.

Our goal is to collect and destroy more cars.
Only higher-level tow hooks can tow higher-level cars.

Play a fun arcade game in Pretty Sheep Run. You guide an adorable little sheep dashing across endless platforms. Keep your sheep running while cleverly avoiding dangerous traps. Control your sheep running to shoot different numbered doors. Change the numbers into positive numbers. Thus increasing the gun's DMG, ATK SPD, etc. Reach the finish line and shoot farther to get rewards. Keep buying guns and merging the same two guns to get upgrades. Your sheep will get higher attack guns. Simple and easy to use, cute and fun graphics make every game relaxing and stress relieving! Whether you love matching, merging, or a sprinkle of shooting action, this game has it all in one adorable arcade adventure! Can you guide the prettiest sheep to challenge further distances? Play now and see!

Get ready for an epic adventure in War Robots Merge, the ultimate mecha battle game. Immerse yourself in a futuristic realm filled with advanced technology, stunning mecha designs, and intense combat scenes. Experience the thrill of high-quality graphics and immerse yourself in an immersive gaming experience. Play now and prove your skills in the arena!

The end is near. The world is no longer peaceful. In this game full of gunfights, zombies, and strategic challenges, you'll battle the evil zombies. Solving number puzzles to unleash your tactical genius. In Last War Survival, you'll play as a survivor in a world ravaged by a zombie virus. Use your gun to avoid zombie attacks. Solve math problems and number puzzles to enhance your combat abilities. Drop bullets where the multiplier is the largest and you'll get tons of bullets to attack hordes of zombies. You can use bombs or rockets to attack enemies in critical situations. Enjoy shooting battles and mathematical puzzles. Show your excellent shooting skills and good strategic thinking to kill zombies. Start your life-and-death survival challenge.

Fishdom Online is a casual game full of fun and creativity. Various gameplay and mini-games bring you a rich gaming experience. Here includes elements such as puzzles, merges, mini-games and collections to make every game challenging and fun. Enjoy relaxing leisure time and improve your skills and strategic abilities through a variety of tasks and challenges.
Protect the seashore from the invasion of enemies. Use all the weapons to stop the invasion of soldiers from the sea and from the air.

Cloak Master-Shooter Run allows you to show your shooting and running skills in an exciting environment! In this casual game, you will be transformed into a mysterious hero. Navigate through different scenarios, avoid obstacles and complete challenges.

Step into the exciting world of TankCraft – War Tank Battles, where creativity meets nervous warfare! Become a master tank crafter and commander as you design your powerful war machine and lead it into epic battles.

Come to soar through the skies in Energy Superman 3D! This exciting arcade game lets you become a powerful superhero. Your mission is to save the city from monstrous threats. Collect energy orbs, avoid obstacles, and achieve the highest score possible!

Dive into the clever world of Screw Sort-Pin Puzzle, where logic and strategy come together! Your task is to sort the colorful screws, click three screws of the same color as the glass, the glass will be shot. You need to pull pins in the right order to avoid chaos!

Welcome to Capybara Screw Jam! This is a cute and brain-teasing puzzle game. You’ll join a lovable capybara on a journey of problem-solving and strategy. With simple gameplay and increasing challenges, it’s the perfect game for anyone who loves casual puzzles and brain workouts. Your goal is to help the capybara solve various puzzle challenges.

Sheep Sort Puzzle: Sort Color is a game of luck, that requires strategic thinking and careful observation. In this game, you are presented with a grid filled with colorful sheep. Your goal is to organize the sheep according to their colors. As you progress through the levels, the difficulty increases, with more sheep of different colors added to the grid. Are you up for the challenge?

Begin a fun battle like never before in Space Survival - Rainbow Friends Monster! You’re in a mysterious space station overrun by terrifying rainbow monsters. Your task is to escape and rescue your friends. Use your gun to begin the battle. Avoid enemy attacks and unleash shooting combos against waves of enemies. Collect pill bottles to increase your health, choose skills to increase your gun's damage, range, etc. Every level is a new battle for survival! Unlock more cool guns to increase damage, rate, bullet speed, and more! Defeat rainbow monsters, avoid their attacks, and escape the space station! Play now and prove your skills.

Step into the fiery forge of Blade Forge 3D, the ultimate 3D simulation casual game. You become the legendary blacksmith. Craft epic weapons from scratch. After matching opponents, choose your own mold and craft your own sword. Temper the sword by forging the blade between the flames. Once completed, the sword will be used to test itself against your opponent. Serious polishing to boost your damage value.

This is a casual puzzle water splashing game!
The game starts simple and gradually becomes complex and challenging.
Rich and charming levels and various combinations of props make classic puzzle games look brand new!

Want to conquer the world? In Evony: The King's Return, step into a vast universe of war and zombie attacks. Command an army and use powerful weapons and guns to attack the enemy. Keep moving your soldiers, shoot digital doors, and expand your army! Keep shooting to get the gun. Face endless zombie waves with your shooting skills and unlock powerful weapons. Get gold to upgrade your ATK SPD or Range! Enjoy a fun shooting arcade game. New updates, events, maps, and heroes keep the excitement going month after month! Come and experience this war strategy masterpiece that has made millions of players around the world go crazy!

There are various food cards in the game, each showing a different type of food. You need to sort similar foods by placing them on corresponding plates to pass each level. In this kitchen, logical thinking is needed to sort the cards into limited spaces on the board to prepare various dishes. You can only place ingredients on the same cards or on blanks. Vegetables, meat or other ingredients required for a recipe are displayed at the top of the board. To be able to process the product, you must place at least ten identical cards on one of the lower storage spaces. You can draw new cards using the "Send" button. But be careful - the stack can hold only a limited number of cards. If all slots are full, the game is over.

Toilet Paper Jam is here. Can you save the entire restroom in this hilarious and brain-bending mess? This is a casual puzzle game full of fun, challenge, and satisfying brain teasers. Sort and unravel the jammed toilet paper rolls that are tangled in the most absurd ways. Match similar rolls of toilet paper and use different lengths of paper properly. The unused paper will be hung on the paper towel rack. You can also use props like Clear, Pointed, or Refresh when you encounter difficulties. Progressive levels that go from funny to fiendishly clever. Whether you're taking a break or need a quick mental boost, this game is the perfect way to make you smile, think, and maybe even laugh out loud!

At the start of the game, several simple patterns will appear. These patterns are secured with screws, and players need to press the wrench button to remove the screws. As the wrench unscrews more screws, subsequent levels will become more difficult. Use your brain to unscrew and collect more wrenches.

Prepare to dive into the gloriously dumb, colorful world of Meme Battle: Monster Merge - a game so absurdly fun, it’ll melt your brain (in the best way possible). If you love mashing things together, watching weird little freaks evolve, and unleashing pure, unhinged destruction, this is your new obsession.

iTileZen Sort Puzzle is a fresh and addictive puzzle game that blends the strategic color sorting mechanics with the satisfying tile-matching gameplay. Moves colorful tiles to complete objectives before time runs out! Whether you love logic puzzles or fast-paced matching challenges, this game offers the best of both worlds.

In the classic connection mode, you need to stretch the bodies of cartoon cats and other cute pets to fill all the blank grids. Note that their bodies can be extended infinitely, but they must not be knotted or crossed! The specially designed Backyard mode is even more interesting! Tap the green circle and your virtual pet will give you gold coins as a reward. After accumulating enough gold coins, you can also go to the pet store to buy all kinds of thoughtful things for your furry children - from nutritious snacks, and funny toys to exquisite food bowls, and cat scratching boards, everything is available! Simple and easy-to-use operation combined with a fresh and cute painting style can not only exercise logical thinking but also enjoy healing time. Whether you are an animal lover or a puzzle master, this creative game will make you love it! Come and embark on a wonderful connection adventure with these cute pets!

Bridge Go Animal Rescue is a skill-based free online game where you long-press to start building a bridge. Control the time you spend building the bridge based on the distance between your animal and the next tower. The longer you touch, the longer the bridge will be. Avoid bridges that are too long or too short, otherwise, the structure will collapse and you will have to start over!

Room Sort Floor Plan is a fun creative puzzle game with elements of sorting and design. In this casual game, you’ll go through proper sorting and organization. Designing the perfect layout for every room. Rearrange the floor plan to create your unique home. Each level is a jigsaw puzzle challenge. Each room is connected by a door. So you need to place them perfectly to create a coherent layout. Finish in a limited time and get a reward. Unlock more rooms, plan your layout and decorate more furniture. As you advance, the levels become more complex. More items and different room styles offer continuous fun and challenges. Relaxing casual style for any time to relax and play.

Ready to begin a fantastic match-3 puzzle adventure? Dream Mania - Happy Match is a fun puzzle game that you won't be able to stop playing. It's easy to play, yet the challenging level design. It's a casual game you don't want to miss! Match 3 or more identical items to clear the board and hit your level goals. Each level has unique missions: collect objects, break blocks, and beat move limits. Unlock and use special boosters to help you pass the level. Create powerful combos with chain reactions for massive score boosts! Dreamy visuals and joyful sound effects for a mood-lifting experience. Come into this fantasy world, use your intelligence to match the pleasure, and the best choice to kill the boring time is here!

Ready to push your brain to the limit? Welcome to Water Pour Jam, the fun sort puzzle game that will test your brain and matching skills. Here you will be confronted with colorful cups. Use your logic and observation to pour liquids of the same color into the same bottle so that the colors match perfectly! Get the juice right. Don't go over the red line. Or you will fail. Each level challenges your logical thinking. One wrong move and you’ll be stuck in a colorful jam. You can use props such as Full, Move, or Disruption when you are in trouble. Plan your moves, solve the puzzle, and enjoy the beautiful moment when the colors match perfectly. So what are you waiting for? Dive into the world of color and strategy.

Enter Flower Jam is a vibrant casual match game with colorful flowers and exciting puzzles. You aim to complete the level by swapping flowers and eliminating them by getting six petals of the same color! Place petals of the same color together to make six petals to eliminate. Get props to help you eliminate tons of flowers. Enjoy explosive combos and satisfying effects. Use your strategy to get a high score. Upgrade flowers to progress faster. Want to test your matching skills? Jump in and let the flower jam fun begin!

MahjongMasterChallenge packs many handcrafted mahjong layouts into one fun puzzle journey. Your goal: clear the board by matching identical or coherent tiles. For example, chow: Combine two pairs into a sequence to clear. Kong: Combine two pairs into four of a kind to clear.

Want a fun 3D puzzle that’s strangely relaxing? In ScrewSortPuzzle:PinJam3D, you’ll remove every screw, sort colorful pins, and match them to the right slots without causing a jam! You will have to keep matching the screws of the right color and put them in the box of the corresponding color. Rotate the board to spot the screws you can safely loosen first. You can experience remove screw mode.

Join the Age of Apes Run, the fun running game of the ape generation. In this fun run game, you're not just any runner. You're a futuristic ape dashing through a chaotic jungle city. Collect more bananas to upgrade your ape hero and unlock cool costumes and gadgets! Meanwhile, you use bananas to get more advanced partners to help you defeat your enemies at the finish line. Each level is more nervous than the last. Race against time, avoid crazy traps, and show your reflexes in this high-speed jungle adventure. The time of the apes has come. Are you ready to open this mad running?

Ready to start a 3D puzzle thats both magical and brain-teasing? Welcome to Crazy Goods Sort 3D, where chaos meets logic, and your job is to restore order. Here, youll be confronted with a pile of boxes that have been tossed around. Sort the same kinds of items into the correct bins so that they match perfectly.

Nuts Color Sort Puzzle is a fun and relaxing brain teaser that combines vibrant visuals with strategic gameplay. Dive into a world of colorful nuts and bolts, where your mission is to sort the nuts by color onto the correct bolts.

With intuitive drag-and-drop controls and increasingly complex levels, this game offers the perfect balance between relaxation and mental challenge. Whether you play during a quick break or for hours on end, each level will test your logic and bring satisfaction with every perfect sort.

Game Features:

🌈 Thousands of colorful, progressive levels

🧠 Brain-training gameplay with strategic elements

🎮 Easy to learn, perfect for all ages

🏆 Unlock rewards and achievements

🔁 Replay levels to improve your best moves

Get ready to test your sorting skills and immerse yourself in this uniquely satisfying color sorting puzzle game!

Looking for a battle royale game that’s more laughter than gunfire? Run Guys: Knockout Royale is your perfect pick. One of the absolute best battle royale games if you love chaos, color, and pure fun! Run, jump and dash your way through obstacle platforms. Each round features new, wacky traps - spinning doors, bouncing pads, and more. The game combines reflexes, logic, and timing. Make it to the final round and grab the crown to become the ultimate champion! Challenge seesaw mode or mountain climbing mode. Keep balance and rush to the finish line. Or be the first to reach the summit and jump onto the crown. Whether you want to pass the time or have a fun battle between friends, this game will satisfy you.
The best car zombie obstacle crash game.

As you progress, encounter cars in 8 different colors, adding complexity to your strategy. Use powerful boosters to line up characters by color or shuffle vehicles, clearing the way more efficiently. Test your logic, think fast, and rescue passengers.

Triple Tile Twister: Match Game is a relaxing puzzle with a twist on mahjong. Clear the board by matching groups of three identical tiles. ?✨ Strategically select tiles to move to the holding area, which holds up to 7 tiles. Create sets of three to clear them, but watch out! ? If the area fills with unmatched tiles, the game ends. Enjoy soothing graphics and relaxing gameplay—perfect for unwinding! ? Great for both mahjong fans and newcomers! ?

Sort Games Challenge is a puzzle game. Here you can challenge yourself and choose from multiple modes, not limited to one. Your goal is to complete the mission within a limited time to pass the level. Dont underestimate this game, its still very difficult to pass. Come and challenge!

Get ready to tidy up the shelves in Shelf Sweep! Dive into a fun and addictive sorting puzzle game where your goal is to clean up messy shelves layer by layer. Only the outermost layer of items is visible—clear them by matching three identical items, and reveal the hidden treasures beneath!

Ready to stretch your brain and have a blast? Color Block Jam is the perfect block puzzle game to challenge your mind. This relaxing puzzle game invites you to drag and drop colorful blocks. Match them correctly to clear the space. Can you match all the blocks correctly? Colorful cubes give you super comfortable visual enjoyment! Whether you're a casual lover or a puzzle master, this game is your new go-to puzzle game. Jump in now and see how high you can score!

Build and upgrade your ultimate army of turrets in Tiny Tower! Strategically place powerful turrets to unleash epic forces like fire, frost, multi-shots, and explosions, fending off waves of incoming monsters. Earn coins by destroying enemies, upgrade your turrets, unlock crazy combo skills, and dominate the battlefield. Can you construct the strongest turret fortress and defend it to victory?

Enjoy an addictive stacking adventure. In Blocks Stack Rush, you’ll control a little block character running and begin a fun pixelated journey. Collect blocks, stack them high and race against time to build the perfect picture. You need to align each block and keep putting together the complete picture.

Join this new puzzle challenge and witness intellectual battles with wooden blocks arranged in chaotic order. The further you progress through the levels, the more complex and intricate the tasks become. By dismantling the complicated structures, you can move forward and create the room of your dreams. The game offers a 3D visual experience, multiple levels, solid physics, and simple controls.

This is an interesting puzzle casual game.

Help all the animals leave the grass to win.

The difficulty of the game levels gradually increases. How many levels can you pass? Come and give it a try!

Welcome to Age of Apes Unblocked, where monkeys race like never before. This is a racing game. Enjoy the unblocked games genre, get online anytime and have a blast! Control your monkey to keep collecting bananas of the corresponding color! Raise your level and defeat opponents who are lower than you! Then cross the bridge to the next section. Eliminate the boxes to get to the finish line. Quick tap to attack the boss. Upgrade your Move SPD, Absorb Range, Exp. Constantly challenge the high score to become the strongest gorilla. Unblocked games can be played without an internet connection, easy to play with zero pressure! Suitable for anyone who loves racing games, especially for those who like funny, exciting and creative gameplay!

Welcome to Train Artillery Adventure, an exciting game combining shooting, merging, and upgrading! In this game, you control a powerful artillery train, traveling through various battle zones and defeating zombies. Control the artillery turret on your train, aim precisely, and fire powerful shots at the zombies.
Match tiles and solve fun puzzles with a charming farm-themed twist!

The multiplayer motorcycle race has begun. You need to control your motorcycle in the multiplayer motorcycle obstacle race and avoid obstacles on the way. Use different terrains to quickly surpass and defeat opponents to become the fastest champion!
The best car road simulation game.

Swordsman Adventure is a thrilling adventure game where you wield your sword freely on the battlefield to complete a series of missions. In this role-playing game, you control your soldier to attack enemies of different hit points.

Welcome to Survive Squad, a hot survival game that combines Strategy and Role-Playing. In a world full of crises, you will be the commander of the squad. Lead your Heroes against endless enemies! Use your wits and strategy to survive the battlefield. Collect and lay out your weapons in your Backpack System. Merge weapons of the same type for upgrades.

In Blob Hero, you become a brave hero facing endless waves of enemies and monsters! This survival game offers a true rogue adventure experience. You control a blob hero, choose basic skills and upgrade to survive.

Welcome to Screw Sort 3D: Screw Puzzle! This game will take you into a challenging and fun world of screw sorting! If you're a fan of puzzle games, you can't miss out on this exciting 3D screw puzzle game. It tests your logical thinking and provides a relaxing experience. You'll face a pile of mixed-up screws. Each level presents a different sorting task. Every screw and puzzle combination is carefully designed to bring you colorful scenes. The game’s environments are perfect for an office puzzle. Try the crew pin jam puzzle and enjoy this creative and challenging game!

Want to become the world's best airport manager? Come to have an exciting airport game that combines strategy and pure fun in the Airport Simulator: Plane Tycoon. It’s one of the best idle games and management games. Hire staff to keep everything running even when you're offline. The more you automate, the more efficient it gets!

Soldier Run Evolution is a fun run game and one of the best games of 2025 you simply can’t miss. This isn’t just another running game. Every second counts and every power-up makes you stronger. Each run is unique with randomly generated levels full of excitement. Join one of the best game 2025 picks and experience nervous action.

Color Block Jam is an ultimate online puzzle game where players have to move different colored blocks to the correct door of the corresponding color. The main objective is to clear the board by removing blocks in the least number of moves. Try to get the highest score to unlock new challenges. Join now to conquer the levels and train your intelligence!

Ready to join the most creative and hilarious Fight Party ever? Welcome to Draw Weapon - Fight Party, a wild blend of fighting game action and crazy imagination. Enter the arena where creativity meets chaos. Smash your enemies with your hand-drawn madness and show off your artistic skills. Come to play one of the fighting games unblocked. Draw your way to victory. Join the craziest Fight Party now and prove you’re the best Weapon Artist.
Match the bus to passengers, fill the bus in this challenging colorful adventure

Enter one of the fun boat games in the Speedboat: Water Shooting. Begin a nervous water shooting game. Drive your powerful speedboat through the choppy waves of the ocean, facing wave after wave of enemy challenges. In the new third person shooter game, you'll control a heavily armed speedboat. Shoot enemies and avoid their attacks. Defeat enemies to earn upgrades and powerful weapons. Jump into the action, feel the water shooting challenge, and become a true speedboat warrior!
Explore the wonders of the galaxy in Galaxy Astro Match! Match, conquer challenges, and build your unique cosmic world!

The princess is in trouble. Only you can save her. Welcome to Princess Rescue Fruit Connect, an addictive fruit merge game mixed with classic match 3 puzzle gameplay. And starring your favorite pretty pretty princess. Enjoy a pretty pretty princess game. This fruit merge match 3 game is perfect for casual puzzle lovers who enjoy colorful, fun, and magical adventures.
Solve a variety of dynamic puzzles that require strategic planning and quick thinking to clear traffic.

Meet the craziest zombie shootout ever. Enjoy one of the most nervous arcade shooting games in the Zombie Shooting King. Play first person shooter games unblocked and constant fighting. Shoot accurately and clear all the enemies. Do you have what it takes to survive the zombie onslaught?

Use your brain power to sort the cars by color, transport cannonballs to defeat the snake, and rescue the girl.

Game features：
1.The gameplay is simple and easy to use.

2.Unlock new levels and unlock new characters.

3.The game screen is lively and interesting, allowing you to release stress.

Enter the wonderful arcade game in the Mob Handler. As a mob handler, face many waves of enemies. Beat the incoming mob by shooting. Use your math skills to calculate the maximum value and go through the gates that boost your skills. You will test your reflexes, strategic planning, and quick thinking. Shooting Ammo, Atk, etc.

Game features：
1.The game combines the most fascinating puzzle solving methods to activate your brain to solve problems.

2.The gameplay of the game's unlimited levels allows you to immerse yourself in the world of puzzle solving.

3.There are many cute dolls waiting for you to unlock in the exhibition hall.

This is an interesting casual game.

Control the water droplets to walk on the paper, and you can draw various colors and complete the pattern.

There are various interesting patterns, making painting simple and fun!

"Extreme Cascading Racing Arcade where you must collect parts to assemble a car. Start the race on foot, then obtain a wheel, followed by a bicycle, then a car. Skillfully maneuver between traps, avoid dangers, jump off cliffs, perform deadly somersaults, and reach the treasures at the finish line."
This maintains the dynamic, action-oriented tone of the original while accurately conveying the gameplay mechanics and progression. The terms "cascading" and "somersaults" preserve the technical elements, while "treasures at the finish line" adds narrative flair.
Classic driving simulation games. Fresh and simple game screen. Simple operation, easy to control. Collect more bricks. Through more levels, build all kinds of castles.
This is a popular hand game recently, magic play, this game belongs to a duel type game, casual games, you can play your offensive ability and painting ability, play your imagination to create.
The crazy snail races along Tenman, can you win the championship?
Beach beauty recently encountered strange things, she grew a lot of hair, can you help her clean it?
Now use you finger push all the blocks to destination!Be careful about the obstacles on the road!
Now drive your boat to pick up all the passengers and deliver them to your destination!Don't forget the passengers, but also be careful about the boats on the river!

Do you like throwing stuff? Like knives at random spinning targets? Then this is the ultimate challenge for you! Time your actions, aim carefully and become the knife master! Can you beat all the levels? Very simple one-touch gameplay, but challenging to master! Can you collect all the ridiculous knives?

Relax and improve your memory and ability at the same time with the worldwide favourite adaptation of the traditional chinese game Mahjong. Match the correct tiles until you clean the whole game field of the very last tile. Try it as fast as possible to gain a golden star that reflects your perception and skill.

Unblock That is a simple and addictive puzzle game. The goal is to unblock the red block out of the board by sliding the other blocks out of the way. Do it with the minimal amount of moves.  The game comes with 4 difficulties ranging from Beginner to Expert. Unblock That can help you train your brain and keep you mentally fit everyday.

Are you bored in work or school? You need to forget daily stress? This simple and colorfull amalgamate of attention, accuracy and correct timing will help. This game is suitable for anyone, especially those who love to overcome challenges with your wits and agility.

Compete, guess, and conquer in Guess Their Answer - the ultimate trivia showdown! Guess Their Answer is an exciting trivia quiz game where your knowledge and quick thinking are put to the test. Face off against smart CPUs in a battle of wits, with each round featuring three challenging questions from a wide range of topics. Outthink your opponents to earn in-game money, which you can use to unlock cool cosmetics like skins. Plus, take on the daily quiz challenge to prove you’re the best!

This captivating logical drawing game invites lovers of rebuses to have an interesting time and train their intellect by solving dilemmas. Something is missing in each picture. Guess what exactly it is and draw this missing part.

Push the Box game is an addictive and challenging puzzle game. It will help you train your brain. The operation of the game is very simple, move the box pusher by using the four direction buttons: up, down, left and right, push all the boxes to the specified position, the game is considered successful. If you are a fan of matching puzzle games, you will love our game. Keep your brain sharp while relaxing, having fun and relieving stress. Come and enjoy playing this puzzle game!

There was a long queue of passengers at the public station platform with a "car jam" in the parking lot! what to do? Now it's time for the cars to transport passengers, you need to move them...but wait! You need to do it in the right order. Because other cars in the parking lot that become an obstacle! Can you solve this tricky parking puzzle and get all the cars on the road? what are you waiting for? Challenge your brain with this tricky game now!

Welcome to the Wood & Screw Puzzle, where the world of puzzles meets the thrill of fasteners! Embark on a thrilling adventure where bolts, nuts, and wooden puzzles collide in a mind-bending challenge. Dive into a world filled with conundrums, where every turn reveals a new twist in the game.

Become a legendary kunai master in this thrilling combination of dynamic gameplay and classic ninja action. Play offline and enjoy the freedom to dive into the adventure whenever you want. Slice through foes, overcome obstacles, and set out on an epic ninja quest without boundaries. Will you seize the blade and claim your place as the ultimate ninja warrior?

Harvest Store Sorting is a puzzle game set in a pastoral world where you need to sort harvested fruits on shelves. Place the same fruits together until each shelf contains only one type of fruit. The game is fun and engaging, with each level featuring differently shaped shelves and varying numbers of them. Use your sorting skills to organize the shelves neatly within the limited space. If you encounter difficulties, you can also use tools to help you pass the levels more easily.

Space Blast is a 2D game full of action arcade game where your piloting skills and strategic thinking are key to navigating relentless waves of meteors. Command a powerful spaceship equipped with advanced weapons and take on the challenge of protecting the galaxy from incoming threats.

Do you like logic games in the style of "Pipeline"? Then don't miss the chance to spend your leisure time interestingly with the next puzzles of this genre. This time, you will become an electrician and take care of restoring the power supply. Properly distribute the missing components so that the electricity reaches the appliance and it starts working.

Welcome to Beach Volley Clash! This vibrant and energetic beach sports game takes you to a lively beach arena. You’ll face off against powerful opponents. Use your skills and quick reflexes to hit the ball precisely and win every match!

Welcome to Zombie Rage: Survival World, the ultimate zombie-mowing adventure! 🌍🧟‍♂️ Take control of powerful harvesters and clear fields overrun by relentless waves of zombies. Your mission?
